{"tid":2006513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(海軍入球)左營艦輪機長「酒後大戰」女士官 違紀軍士官撤職汰除","createTime":"2020-05-07T23:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T01:59:47.000Z","uid":47492,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9d5fe0d577c202262260a7fe6e962b542ea5865a","tid":2006513,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T23:13:58.000Z","msg":"〔記者涂鉅旻／台北報導〕海軍基隆級驅逐艦左營艦近期傳出不當性別關係與舉止事件，該艦男性副艦長、輪機長及一名女士官違規在艦上飲酒，甚至後二者還在艦上發生性行為，對此，海軍艦隊指揮部表示，單位獲報後主動查處，已依「刑懲併行」原則，針對違反「性別分際」及「營內飲酒」，分別予以撤職及兩大過懲處汰除，並移送法辦。"},{"pid":"02cc2abf55750310cf86011ea45261c8fbcdaaf6","tid":2006513,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T23:14:18.000Z","msg":"外傳此事發生於上月中旬，至今已有半個月，而單位獲報後立即查處，對相關人員祭出懲處，海軍司令劉志彬更震怒要求嚴辦。<br />\n<br />\n海軍艦指部強調，艦指部秉持「毋枉毋縱」原則，凡肇生重大違法犯紀案件者，本「留優汰劣」原則嚴懲不貸。將持續落實軍法紀要求，並加強內部管理，以杜絕類案肇生"},{"pid":"21ba3e40e75278b91872448064943e0fe3c2ba67","tid":2006513,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T23:15:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3158708\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3158708&d=kJsi%2B77Adq7yP7dZlTZe0G7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=3a3ba893\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3158708&h=f673caac\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3158708</a>"},{"pid":"b27bfcb4da15346b80a8b7183f984caf34380ea3","tid":2006513,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T23:17:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41aaab1599bf4adacbb7f1f8f4da706dbde0f422","tid":2006513,"uid":37912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T23:38:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98f184c507bc311492471a98ae2bcaa4b6051ea7","tid":2006513,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c